ction, please provide a scientific estimate of the reasonable range of direct construction and installation costs for this sunroom. In addition, explain the applicable technical standards, material performance specifications, and the cost rationale employed.'}], 'model': 'nex/nex-n1.1', 'max_tokens': 20000, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.3}}
