ysis must cover the impact of pricing strategies, product mix, and changes in the supply-demand dynamics of traditional storage products."}], 'model': 'nex/nex-n1.1', 'max_tokens': 20000, 'response_format': {'type': 'json_object'}, 'temperature': 0.3}}
